title: S13 Ep23: The Naked Witch: Witchcraft in the Modern World
itunes:title: The Naked Witch: Witchcraft in the Modern World
description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS stands before The Naked Witch discussing Witchcraft in the Modern World with famed witch Fiona Horne.

From high atop a car park in the faraway and hurricane riddled St. Thomas in the US Virgin Isles Fiona Horne chats about Magic, her amazing life & gifts and the power of witchcraft and what it all means.

Get her book here: Amazon.com/shop/darknessradio

Visit her site here: www.FionaHorne.com
